imdb.plot outline: The Löwenzahn offshoot Löwenzenzchen is aimed at preschool children. In this series it is especially about Fritz's dog Keks. While Fritz is on the road, Keks experience their own adventures, thus revealing nature to children between the ages of 3 to 6.
